            <div class="main-content">
                <!-- Intro Section -->
                <div class="intro-section">
                    <p>Moving to a new apartment in Chicago? New City Moving provides affordable moving services
                        throughout Chicago and the surrounding suburbs. Since 2009, our trusted apartment movers have
                        helped thousands of residents with every stage of their relocation. From packing and loading to
                        transport and storage, we'll protect your belongings and get you settled into your new home
                        right on schedule.</p>

                    <p>You may be dreading your upcoming apartment move for several reasons. Apartments are often
                        smaller spaces with fewer entrances and other tricky moving requirements. Moving in or out of an
                        apartment may involve climbing long flights of stairs, navigating hallways, or continuously
                        squeezing your belongings into and out of an elevator.</p>

                    <p>New City Moving Chicago apartment movers are here to take all the stress out of your next
                        apartment move. Our team of professionals will handle every aspect, from creating a detailed
                        plan to packing, unpacking, loading, unloading and more. We'll save you valuable time and energy
                        for an affordable price.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Challenges Section -->
                <section>
                    <h2>We Are Apartment Moving Specialists</h2>
                    <p>We're the No. 1 choice for expert small movers in Chicago and surrounding areas. Apartment moves
                        include numerous challenges, but our professionals are ready to get the job done efficiently,
                        safely and affordably.</p>

                    <p>The following are a few of the many difficulties apartment moves can present:</p>

                    <div class="challenge-grid">
                        <div class="challenge-card">
                            <h4><span class="challenge-icon">🏢</span> Stairs and Elevators</h4>
                            <p>Many of Chicago's older buildings do not have elevators. Our professionals have the
                                skills and strength to move your items, no matter how many flights of stairs are in the
                                way.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="challenge-card">
                            <h4><span class="challenge-icon">📦</span> Large Items, Small Space</h4>
                            <p>We're experts in securely wrapping furniture and belongings to keep them safe when
                                getting big items into and out of compact spaces.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="challenge-card">
                            <h4><span class="challenge-icon">🛡️</span> Wall Protection</h4>
                            <p>Renting means you likely paid a security deposit, and we want you to get it back. We'll
                                protect the walls while moving to prevent any damage.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="challenge-card">
                            <h4><span class="challenge-icon">🔄</span> Tight Corners</h4>
                            <p>Chicago apartments often feature long hallways and tight corners. Our experts know how to
                                safely maneuver your furniture around all obstacles.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="challenge-card">
                            <h4><span class="challenge-icon">🚗</span> Parking Considerations</h4>
                            <p>Lack of parking near an apartment building can cause problems. Our experts know Chicago
                                Department of Transportation requirements and will handle permits.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="challenge-card">
                            <h4><span class="challenge-icon">⏰</span> Time Constraints</h4>
                            <p>We work efficiently to meet building move-in/move-out time requirements and minimize
                                disruption to neighbors and property management.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <p>New City Moving Chicago apartment movers are equipped to perform efficient and safe apartment
                        moves whether you're on the bottom floor or the top. Let us handle all the heavy lifting, moving
                        requirements and challenges so you can rest easy and enjoy the city.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Process Section -->
                <section>
                    <h2>Our Apartment Moving Process</h2>
                    <p>At New City Moving, we handle all types of apartment and condo relocations. Whether you're moving
                        to or from a high-rise, a studio apartment or luxury condo, our experienced movers make your
                        relocation easy and stress-free.</p>

                    <div class="process-steps">
                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">1</div>
                            <div class="step-content">
                                <h4>Get a Free Quote</h4>
                                <p>Receive a straightforward, free apartment moving quote with no hidden charges.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">2</div>
                            <div class="step-content">
                                <h4>Schedule Your Apartment Move</h4>
                                <p>Arrange a convenient time and we'll accommodate your building's requirements.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">3</div>
                            <div class="step-content">
                                <h4>Packing and Loading</h4>
                                <p>Choose from full or partial packing services using professional-grade packing
                                    materials.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">4</div>
                            <div class="step-content">
                                <h4>Safe Transportation</h4>
                                <p>Relax as we transport your belongings to your apartment in Chicago or the surrounding
                                    area.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="step-item">
                            <div class="step-number">5</div>
                            <div class="step-content">
                                <h4>Unloading and Unpacking</h4>
                                <p>Get settled into your apartment as we unpack your items to make ready for an easy
                                    set-up.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <p>When you hire our apartment movers, you get the benefit of years of experience handling stairs,
                        elevators and small spaces. We'll take care of the planning and complicated logistics required
                        for a stress-free relocation.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Services Included Section -->
                <section>
                    <h2>What's Included in Our Apartment Moving Services</h2>
                    <p>Apartment moving can be a challenging, even frustrating experience. From building logistics
                        issues and limited loading zones to strict move-out times and coordinating with building
                        management, relocating to or from an apartment is far easier when you partner with the
                        professionals.</p>

                    <div class="services-list">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Light furniture disassembly and reassembly</li>
                            <li>Short-term and long-term storage</li>
                            <li>Insurance coverage for belongings</li>
                            <li>Protective padding for safety</li>
                            <li>Elevator reservation coordination</li>
                            <li>Building access permits</li>
                            <li>Professional packing materials</li>
                            <li>Specialty item handling</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <p>And when your apartment move needs a specialty solution, our highly-rated local moving services
                        can accommodate most requests.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- FAQ Section -->
                <section class="faq-section">
                    <h2>Common Questions About Apartment Movers</h2>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <span>How long does it take to complete a small apartment move?</span>
                            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <div class="faq-answer-content">
                                A small apartment move typically takes around 2–4 hours, depending on the amount of
                                belongings and complexity of the move. An apartment relocation may require more time,
                                based on factors like elevator availability, parking restrictions and so on.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <span>Can apartment movers handle tight hallways and stairs?</span>
                            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <div class="faq-answer-content">
                                Experienced apartment movers can handle small doorways, narrow hallways and tricky
                                staircases without causing damage to belongings or the building. Movers may use
                                equipment like furniture dollies and moving straps to help navigate apartment buildings.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <span>Can I pack belongings myself for an apartment move?</span>
                            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <div class="faq-answer-content">
                                Absolutely—customers can pack their own belongings for an apartment move or choose a
                                partial packing service. However, when you want to protect fragile items and save time
                                during a relocation, it's a good idea to choose a full packing service.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

